test_even_range:
assert [81, 83, 85] == []
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: 81
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [81, 83, 85]
test_all_one_range:
assert [81, 82, 83, 84, 85] == [1, 1, 1, 1]
  At index 0 diff: 81 != 1
  Left contains one more item: 85
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1, 1, 1]
  + [81, 82, 83, 84, 85]
